Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:09.01,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}I had lost my way during my journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:17.02,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Only my soul was wandering, while I stood still.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.02,0:00:25.28,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}But right now, I'm walking to a distant place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:33.53,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}That's right, ever since I met you on this road.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:41.96,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}The travellers witnessed the song, the forbidden song,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:52.72,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}And I became attached to it as I heard it alone with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.72,0:01:00.81,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}If the world I saw in my dreams exists somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:09.20,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Let's go search for it, beyond the winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:13.37,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Whether it's a freezing dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:17.58,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}A dry midday,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.58,0:01:21.75,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}A shivering night,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.75,0:01:28.00,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}or the ends of the Earth, let's go and see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:40.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.93,0:01:44.49,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,He's another accomplice for today's job.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.49,0:01:47.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Martin Liebert from the Remerio Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.58,0:01:50.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm Nora Allent.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.07,0:01:53.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us set off, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.47,0:01:56.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Business is like raw fish in a kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.63,0:02:01.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It means it'll be all for naught if we don't act quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:18.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think it'll go well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.95,0:02:31.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There'll be no tomorrow for us if we fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.91,0:02:43.95,Chapter Name Title Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Wolf and Young Pack
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.30,0:02:49.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.57,0:02:51.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun hasn't even set yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.89,0:02:53.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:55.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I will go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.12,0:02:57.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Please catch up with me as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:00.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:01.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:04.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,He just doesn't know how dangerous it is for a shepherd to travel at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.31,0:03:09.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,He's shouldering Remerio's future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:11.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:27.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The stars are pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:29.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:32.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They're prettier where I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:38.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think we could be having such a normal conversation under these circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:43.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be able to hold out if we're pressured all day and night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:45.61,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.82,0:03:50.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow we'll be facing the problematic road.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:09.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like it wouldn't be strange if something just appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:12.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't panic if wolves appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.76,0:04:15.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I will guide you safely to the city for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:23.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,May God protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.87,0:04:36.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:40.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think we'll be okay with the wolves?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:43.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we're already surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:44.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:51.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If{\i0} that happened, I would guarantee your safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.07,0:04:53.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say the same for anyone else, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:04:59.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be problematic if everyone isn't safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.12,0:05:01.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really sure about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:04.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind is blowing in from the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:06.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If there were wolves in the forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:10.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,they would have bared their fangs and the sheep would have realized it already
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:25.45,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a smart dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:28.45,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:29.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.79,0:05:34.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That dog knows about me and is hiding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:35.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:39.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, he should know his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:44.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Nora knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:51.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If we fail at smuggling, then Nora is the one who is least able to justify her actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:55.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We could keep quiet about it and escape, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:59.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you're so weak against blonde girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:01.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you what punishments we could receive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:05.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,She won't be able to stand them with that small body of hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:11.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should protect her with all your might so that it doesn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:15.49,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.67,0:06:36.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be great if they don't appear from here on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:39.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Ah, yes, really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.74,0:06:43.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If we set off at dawn, we'll reach Ramtra by noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:46.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And then it'll finally be my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:49.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go and sleep to prepare myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:53.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,May you sleep well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:36.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back, Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:44.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to panic about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:50.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wake up and be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.13,0:08:28.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you drive them away?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:31.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, they've gone further away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:35.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The wolves here are always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:38.91,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't howl or show any signs of attacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:42.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They just watch and stare at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:49.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly is strange that they don't howl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.70,0:09:03.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it goes well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:06.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:11.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:15.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you familiar with wolves, Horo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:21.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:25.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You seemed to have noticed the wolves quite quickly last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:29.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing, just something like instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:30.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:33.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I might have been on guard to some extent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:36.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You just can't rely on men.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:38.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.73,0:09:42.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Ah, no, that's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:45.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then what do you think about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.47,0:09:52.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry, so just say what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:02.91,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a pretty good eye for people!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.28,0:10:12.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, it's strange to ask someone who's travelling with a man if they're familiar with wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:13.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:17.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,By the time night sets, the wolves will have already appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:20.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a cute rabbit like {\i1}you{\i0} right before them, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.75,0:10:27.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way a rabbit who's about to be eaten by wolves every night wouldn't be familiar with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:30.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, um, that's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:33.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a nice reaction!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:36.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's the opposite for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:41.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,My companion is a rabbit who would die from loneliness if I didn't care for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:43.61,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.61,0:10:47.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,it was just a coincidence that I noticed the wolves quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.72,0:10:51.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I had thought you were a shepherd.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.16,0:10:54.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a real surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.26,0:10:59.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Enik seems to be very conscious of you, Horo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:11:02.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's probably because he's fallen for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.61,0:11:05.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Enik has?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.32,0:11:09.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You care for him very much, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.88,0:11:15.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, he probably favors you more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:20.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If he doesn't frolic with others sometimes, his desires will show for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.59,0:11:22.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be blunt sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.65,0:11:24.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll become a good rein.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:30.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's unfaithful to me in the future, I'll do what you told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.13,0:11:31.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.66,0:11:34.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.51,0:11:36.86,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to praise him as much as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.74,0:11:42.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether this job succeeds or fails,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:46.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I will stop being a shepherd.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:51.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel a bit more relieved now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:52.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:26.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You certainly have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:30.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness, I thought it didn't go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:31.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I look that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:35.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you feel nervous carrying such a large amount of gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.75,0:12:37.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.09,0:12:38.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's set off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:45.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like this gold, a shining tomorrow awaits us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.31,0:12:56.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is this really the same road we took?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:13:00.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It just feels very different to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:01.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Enik!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:04.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, let us hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:10.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:13.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they're also on that hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.49,0:13:19.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Will we be alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:22.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but please hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.08,0:13:25.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Enik!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.44,0:13:30.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl is doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:33.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The wolves won't be able to make a move like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:35.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:40.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Wolves won't do anything that will harm a member of their pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:45.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They act carefully by spreading the pack out and slowly cornering their prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:46.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Enik!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:51.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But with their formation,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:53.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,we can turn the tables on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.05,0:13:55.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We can get through at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.75,0:13:58.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,A single wolf won't come and attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:03.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:04.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:17.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Sink or swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:24.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.61,0:14:42.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Youngsters are like that lately, even among humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:46.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones in the forest are the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:51.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:52.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Nora! How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.38,0:14:56.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but I will do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.11,0:14:57.45,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.97,0:15:43.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:46.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I will have to deal with things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:49.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the girl and man go first,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:51.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,you should distance yourself as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:54.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.69,0:15:59.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you it's not a normal wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:04.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If I stay here, the pack won't chase the sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:07.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Their target isn't the sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:10.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What thoughtless obstinacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:12.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What stupid pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.67,0:16:17.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Every one of these youngsters only value themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:24.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if you don't say anything, no one will move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.55,0:16:26.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Cooperation between partners is important, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:33.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We will take care of things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.46,0:16:36.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You two take the gold and continue as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:38.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.55,0:16:40.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, let's leave things to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.51,0:16:43.33,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us meet again at the walls of Rubinheigen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:45.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll all be rich then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.37,0:16:50.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We wish you luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:03.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Distance yourself as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.24,0:17:06.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be troublesome if you're close.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:08.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.11,0:17:14.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you if you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:22.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd kiss you here if you were a good male.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:26.49,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:33.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If possible, I'd like to settle this peacefully, but
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.48,0:17:35.49,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.54,0:17:39.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be naked and cold when we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:40.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be troubled, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.78,0:17:48.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:17:59.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:00.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Nora!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:02.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to let their deaths be in vain?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:04.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Their deaths?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:05.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.21,0:18:09.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us hurry to answer their courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:45.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:51.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a youngster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.23,0:18:54.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You bare your fangs right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:15.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.95,0:19:28.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Lawrence?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.41,0:19:30.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:31.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.96,0:19:33.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We heard about it from Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.93,0:19:37.86,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We were waiting outside the forest for you in case anything were to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:39.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,but you didn't come no matter how long we waited.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:40.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:45.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It began to rain harder, so I was trying to dry off my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:50.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Lawrence, where is your companion?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.59,0:19:52.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:55.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:05.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell you to not think badly of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.98,0:20:10.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the Remerio Company going to betray me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:11.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.36,0:20:16.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt heavy-hearted knowing that there was a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.07,0:20:17.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's fortunate that she isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:21.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be an excuse, but we're hanging off a cliff too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:25.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We must eliminate all the dangers we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:26.86,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'll do what you tell me to?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.47,0:20:30.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone will fall to greed with a large amount of gold before them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:32.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's common sense in the world of business, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.74,0:20:36.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I will let you keep your companion's robe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:44.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It would fill my heart with grief, so I cannot tell you that we may meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.61,0:20:50.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,When I think about what will happen after, I start to feel depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:51.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.26,0:20:52.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it the same with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.92,0:20:55.86,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But, that's the girl this man brought!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.86,0:20:56.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.78,0:21:02.23,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look! If you had stayed still...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:14.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we tie up the girl and leave her here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.57,0:21:16.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We can have the wolves take care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:17.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.59,0:21:19.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,She uses pagan magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.99,0:21:23.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,She'd probably survive even if we tied both her hands and blindfolded her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:25.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, we'll be the ruined ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.79,0:21:28.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's really depressing to have to take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.29,0:21:29.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.57,0:21:31.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:35.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How are we going to finish him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:37.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we stab him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:40.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's better if we kill less.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.10,0:21:41.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.60,0:21:45.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Liebert will yell at us if we don't hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.59,0:21:48.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Your companion is probably dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.96,0:22:19.94,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven apples on the witch's tree
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.94,0:22:25.32,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,With seven seeds to plant inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:30.50,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,In spring time I grew a magic song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.50,0:22:33.24,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Then skipping along,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.24,0:22:35.80,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I sang the song to everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.80,0:22:41.23,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I look at the world through apple eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.23,0:22:46.56,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,And cut myself a slice of sunshine pie
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.56,0:22:51.90,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I danced with the peanuts for the flies
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.90,0:22:54.53,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Till someone had told me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.53,0:22:57.59,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,To say hello for every good-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.59,0:23:02.55,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Saw some sugar stars
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.55,0:23:07.64,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put them in a jar
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.64,0:23:10.21,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.21,0:23:13.65,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh we'll wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.65,0:23:17.51,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little wolf inside a cart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.51,0:23:18.86,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,You say,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.86,0:23:23.15,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,And off I go from June to May
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.15,0:23:29.04,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh we'll wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.04,0:23:32.69,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.54,0:23:44.01,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Wolf and New Journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.20,0:23:49.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Wolf and New Journey.
